songs.title: HIGHEST IN THE ROOM (Demo)*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from snippets

[Chorus: Travis Scott]
Case it's fumes
She fill my mind up with ideas (Straight up)
I'm the highest in the room (I'm the highest, it's lit)
Hope I make it outta here

[Verse: Lil Baby]
Ayy, I just left space, yeah
There ain't no case, yeah
When you balling on the place, yeah
I be careful, don't see no place
That's why I put it 'til the grave, yeah
All my...
...I can feel the Perkies hittin' me
[?]
